    <div class="tn-note">
      <strong>&#x1f4dd; Cultural Note:</strong> If it would appear in your language that the woman was making a statement and then contradicting it, you could reword this as a positive statement. Alternate translation: [Only slacken for me to ride if I tell you to do that]
